# ============================================================
# HFWastelandZ — Secrets Configuration (API keys, passwords)
# File: HFWastelandZ_secrets.conf   (remove .example from the name)
# Location: <profile>\hf_wastelandz\configs\
#
# The mod also writes this template automatically on first boot —
# this copy exists so you can prepare it ahead of time alongside
# the other config files in this folder.
#
# !! SECURITY WARNING !!
# - NEVER commit this file to git
# - NEVER share this file publicly
# - NEVER include it in a mod distribution
# - Each server admin maintains their own copy
#
# HOW TO GENERATE A KEY (run in any terminal):
#   Windows:  python  -c "import secrets; print(secrets.token_hex(32))"
#   Linux:    python3 -c "import secrets; print(secrets.token_hex(32))"
#
# The SAME key goes in two places:
#   1. The gateway's config.py — this server's entry in SERVERS (api_key)
#   2. This file (API_KEY line below)
# Running more than one game server? Each server gets its OWN key —
# never reuse a key across servers.
#
# A generated key is 64 hex characters and looks like this:
#   74eda400e341b42edcaba2c1968811603b248641e50295dbf82dcd5d40e076f0
# That one is a PUBLIC EXAMPLE — never use it. Generate your own.
#
# Without a valid API_KEY, every gateway REST call returns 401.
# Player wallets / inventory will not save.
#
# Format: KEY VALUE (one per line). Comments: # or //
# ============================================================

# --- Gateway API Key ---
# Must match the api_key for this server in the gateway's config.py.
API_KEY REPLACE_WITH_YOUR_ACTUAL_API_KEY
